Looking at the balance sheet, these types of assets would be categorized as "Fixed Assets." Fixed assets represent tangible property, plant, and equipment used in business operations, precisely matching the description in the task.

From the balance sheet, I can see that:
- Fixed Assets have an initial value of 5000000.00 as of 2023-12-31
- Fixed Assets have an end value of 5000000.00 as of 2024-02-05

The appropriate line item is "Fixed Assets" which represents the tangible items described in the task.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '5000000.00', 'end value': '5000000.00'}}
```
